                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10227" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1172</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">261 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">场景为翼：大疆的创新跃迁之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Wings of Scenario: DJI’s Path of Transformative Innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李子彪，韩潇阳，曹辉，陈璐瑶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳市大疆创新科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大疆创新；场景驱动创新；创新生态系统；低空经济；技术迭代；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">DJI; Scenario-Driven Innovation; Innovation Ecosystem; Low-Altitude Economy; Technological Iteration.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以“大疆的创新跃迁之路”为主题，系统梳理了大疆创新从早期技术创业到引领全球无人机产业的成长轨迹，聚焦其“场景驱动创新”核心逻辑。创始人汪滔凭对飞控技术的执着，实现了从航模配件到一体化消费级航拍无人机的跨越。大疆敏锐捕捉到大众对易用、平价航拍设备的需求，推出Phantom系列，迅速打开消费市场并确立行业地位。面对消费市场饱和，团队主动拥抱农业、测绘、应急等新场景，特别是在农业植保领域，通过与科研、产业链及政策、金融等多方协同，推动农业无人机规模化落地。大疆持续产品迭代和生态构建，推动无人机在多行业高效转化。进入“低空经济”时代，大疆顺应政策东风，探索物流、城市管理等新兴场景，不断拓展无人机社会价值边界。案例强调，大疆发展不仅是以场景为核心、需求为导向的技术突破，更是持续跨界创新和生态共建的典范，展现了“融入场景，创造未来”的企业成长逻辑。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case, titled Wings of Scenario: DJI’s Path of Transformative Innovation, systematically traces DJI’s growth from a technology-driven startup to a global leader in the drone industry, highlighting its core logic of scenario-driven innovation. Founder Frank Wang’s persistent pursuit of flight control technology enabled DJI’s leap from model aircraft components to integrated consumer drones. Capturing the public demand for easy-to-use and affordable aerial photography, DJI launched the Phantom series, quickly opening up the consumer market and securing industry leadership. As consumer demand plateaued, DJI proactively embraced emerging scenarios such as agriculture, mapping, and emergency response—especially excelling in agricultural plant protection. By collaborating with research institutions, industrial partners, policymakers, and financiers, DJI facilitated the large-scale application of agricultural drones. It continued iterating its products and building a robust ecosystem to drive cross-industry drone integration. In the era of the “low-altitude economy,” DJI has leveraged favorable policies to explore new domains like logistics and urban management. This case demonstrates that DJI’s success stems not only from technological breakthroughs but from continuously integrating innovation into real-world scenarios—exemplifying how scenario alignment and ecosystem co-creation fuel sustainable growth and redefine industry frontiers.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">需求拉动创新理论；场景驱动创新的内涵；场景驱动创新的战略重点；场景驱动创新与创新生态系统；场景驱动创新的运行机制；场景驱动创新的突出特征；突破性技术创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
